        <p>Retrieves the list of all the forum boards. The output contains 2 objects called <code>pages</code> and <code>list</code>. The <code>list</code> object contains an arraylist of <a href="{{ path('_docs2_responses') }}#forum">forum models</a>. The <code>pages</code> object is an integer number which indicates the amount of pages.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><code>page</code>:  The current set of topics to return. Each set contains at most 20 items. Default value is &quot;1&quot; if not supplied.</li>
        </ul>

